{"tid":1730604,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有個方法可以同黑警談判有機會放到理大手捉","createTime":"2019-11-17T14:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T15:03:57.000Z","uid":334487,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d6e307713f331640e9189aa743a4a6b6a0461c7b","tid":1730604,"uid":334487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T14:07:39.000Z","msg":"首先講清楚我係食飯個時聽到旁邊既人講,係度強烈呼籲所有人唔可好咁做!<br />\n<br />\n個個人話而家要活捉狗既屋企人/直情活捉休班警等等，然後要求立刻放哂所有理大既人士，一個都唔可以垃，唔係會對活捉到既狗不利<br />\n<br />\n而且佢會set時限，可能每15分鐘無回應就會斬手指，跟住斬手，斬腳，挖眼，傷害會不斷升級<br />\n<br />\n仲有佢話如果到時唔妥協照捉理大既人到最後就會殺左佢,而政府會輸哂民意比人話自己人都唔救<br />\n<br />\n嚴重警告大家千其唔好咁做!"},{"pid":"d9886c338998cff185108983c59de4872540feb3","tid":1730604,"uid":334487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T14:08:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a989a16dd79bce4eb4601fe694c52345541a3fd9","tid":1730604,"uid":334487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T14:11:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"998c333ccf1e6928dca14ea8e64a7399ed13b380","tid":1730604,"uid":334487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T14:11:25.000Z","msg":"123"},{"pid":"fd7cd6c69dd4831184ce68bf5e0d260a81c5b7b6","tid":1730604,"uid":334487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T14:12:50.000Z","msg":"推123"},{"pid":"6d2e53b060900b5960a18e2ef89acd1811520686","tid":1730604,"uid":334487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T14:13:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2807d2995e3f3cb51e2c761e612ecba789037f89","tid":1730604,"uid":334487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ef780cf0c1b5df47e73014761651589a84d09ae","tid":1730604,"uid":334487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T14:15:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94b9a3b5134ab2518b610d691ac44eb08c8aed5d","tid":1730604,"uid":334487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T14:16:29.000Z","msg":"推"},